snippet.title: Angelina Jolie is Defending Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard??
snippet.description:
Angelina Jolie is Defending Johnny Depp Against Amber Heard??

The never-ending fight between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard seems to last forever. And after Amber Heard accused him of committing domestic vi*lence during their marriage, multiple celebrities with ties to Johnny Depp have come forward in his defense. 

This is really impressive but Johnny Depp’s other ex-wife and mother of his two children, Vanessa Paradis, his ex-fiancé Winona Ryder, and his former co-star Penelope Cruz have all testified in the actor’s defense. But the one who never liked Johnny’s relationship with Amber was no other but Angelina Jolie. 

#Angelina Jolie #Amber Heard #Johnny Depp
